the  landing,  shipping,  wharfage,  lighterage,  cranage  and 
storage  of  goods,  and  the  use  of  the  Authority’s  vessels 
and vehicles and demurrage thereon;

the  use  of  a  quay,  wharf,  dock,  jetty,  pier,  landing-place, 
foreshore or other property vested in or under the control 
of the Authority;

